General.Name: Cedergrenska AB
General.Description: Cedergrenska AB (publ) provides preschool and post-secondary education services. It operates primary schools, marine polytechnic schools, kindergartens, and gymnasiums, as well as provides teacher trainee programs. The company was founded in 2017 and is based in Stocksund, Sweden.
